Description: IONA blockchain — consensus node daemon (v28.7.0)
 IONA is a high-performance Byzantine Fault Tolerant blockchain node
 with pluggable execution, Cosmos adapter, enterprise RBAC, and
 tamper-evident audit logging.
 .
 This package provides: iona-node binary + systemd unit + default config.
 After install: systemctl enable --now iona-node
